  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1007">
<l>aṟṟārkkoṉ ṟāṟṟātāṉ celva mikanalam </l>
<l>peṟṟā ṭamiyaṇmūt taṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wealth of him who never bestows anything on the destitute is like a woman of beauty growing old without a husband.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
